to have been heavily modified, mo!

rows.label: qst702606_msg0102

rows.label: qst702606_msg0201

Unlike last time, it
collected something, mo!

rows.label: qst702606_msg0302
rows.name: I think Dudan did a good job, mo...

rows.label: qst702606_msg0303

But I want to hear what
Parvi thinks, mo.
